{"tid":2198643,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"preposition用法之多問","createTime":"2020-09-11T13:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T03:00:45.000Z","uid":307927,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"908cf1546849f324397f9a0e41573ddaad5b332b","tid":2198643,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"小弟係英文熱愛者<br />\n但往往被preposition搞到非常苦惱<br />\n希望借呢個貼 同一眾有識之士交流學野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日問題：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQdzsBQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQdzsBQ.png&h=6539d2af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中native speaker 用法係: secret INTO sth<br />\n<br />\nWhat&rsquo;s your secret into convincing Hazard to become a blue.<br />\n<br />\n1. 我想問點解用secret into?<br />\n2. 用secret ABOUT convincing ... or secret OF convincing ... 帶出嚟意義會唔會唔同？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6045166b286473f1b1218ea50b40d8681bf057c4","tid":2198643,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895dc5cf97cc36bcdb510ce7afecf26fdd2afd8c","tid":2198643,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87e9b1a791c5548051b24520b8b3698bdff8478","tid":2198643,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83470bb3c4d3fa0eff2d1ccb70e2e223437ceeb","tid":2198643,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074387a9c986eebd3102a305f323d10d44d9a04