Finspirassion.com%2Fen%2Fprep%2Fsecret&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=f9f29262\" target=\"_blank\">https://inspirassion.com/en/prep/secret</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee33fc08b8770a080fe5cd2e8c12324868d8e8c","tid":2198643,"uid":25652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"Cambridge字典：<br />\n<br />\nInto: enthusiasm, interest<br />\n<br />\nWe use be into to express enthusiasm or strong interest for something:<br />\n<br />\nHe&rsquo;s really into his work.<br />\n<br />\nI&rsquo;m into classical music and Thai food.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然未必關事，但我都同意樓上所講有陣時冇得直譯，secret into 有可能真係表達出問者好有興趣想知到當中原因"},{"pid":"813b9df95c8262b4042631f314bbfdbb16a91f87","tid":2198643,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee33fc08b8770a080fe5cd2e8c12324868d8e8c","tid":2198643,"uid":25652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"Cambridge字典：<br />\n<br />\nInto: enthusiasm, interest<br />\n<br />\nWe use be into to express enthusiasm or strong interest for something:<br />\n<br />\nHe&rsquo;s really into his work.<br />\n<br />\nI&rsquo;m into classical music and Thai food.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然未必關事，但我都同意樓上所講有陣時冇得直譯，secret into 有可能真係表達出問者好有興趣想知到當中原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會係呢個po定時定候問<br />\n<br />\n大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b9fbdfcb15e2e5b044a3b11d81f3edb6f75f8c","tid":2198643,"uid":120431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dacbe61027e9e737b99cbe213d29d51ac65996","tid":2198643,"uid":261236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT